49
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:51,640
 And Josef Franco is Managing Director at World Trade Institute.

50
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:05,480
 Thank you all. Madam Revoltela, let's start with you.

51
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:14,920
 We've seen the benefits for CESI countries in terms of globalization, interconnection, trade.

