01:03:38,840 --> 01:03:46,760
 And I think that's a very important point for the region also because of aging population coming

551
01:03:46,760 --> 01:03:57,000
 up and because of lack of skills that are both lack of skills in terms of specific skills.

552
01:03:57,000 --> 01:04:02,840
 And one particularly that is not only on the region, it's Europe overall is lack of skill

553
01:04:02,840 --> 01:04:06,040
 for the net zero transition and on the digital side.

