01:04:29,240 --> 01:04:35,640
 And what we see is that, in fact, I think everybody who is trying to look at the net zero transition

560
01:04:35,640 --> 01:04:42,680
 is trying to learn about not only -- not only institutions can have the capacity to develop

561
01:04:42,680 --> 01:04:43,880
 internally the skills.

