01:05:23,400 --> 01:05:26,840
 You're not going to name that country?

572
01:05:26,840 --> 01:05:34,200
 I'm looking at the governor.

573
01:05:34,200 --> 01:05:40,360
 But I think that's a much bigger topic.

574
01:05:40,360 --> 01:05:46,920
 And we have a 1:37 -- I think we can organize a different conference.

575
01:05:48,360 --> 01:05:50,120
 Okay.

576
01:05:50,120 --> 01:05:54,760
 I thank you very much for your time, for all your observations.

577
01:05:54,760 --> 01:05:59,160
 And I can only invite you to lunch.

